        <h3>Get to know your dog even better.</h3>
        <p>Welcome to your Good Dog Program. Dogs are amazing! They can also be stressful.
            Over the next 6 weeks you will foster a new relationship with your dog. Dogs
            thrive with structure and routine. Dogs who act out or misbehave simply just
            don't know better. There is a lot to learn on your journey - for you and your
            pup. This week you will lean the basics of <a>How Dogs Think</a> and the two
            most essential commands, <a>Sit</a> and <a>Come</a>. You'll be amazed at how
            much progress can be made in one week. We KNOW you love your dog, you wouldn't
            be here if you didn't. That being said, we promise you that after the completion
